[src:arangodb/documentation] HA/DR, RBAC, elastic scaling, and deployment flexibility **built into the platform**, not bolted on afterward.
[src:arangodb/documentation] Horizontal scale across graph, vector, document, key-value, and search.
[src:arangodb/documentation] Query, index, and analyze enterprise data in real-time.
[src:arangodb/documentation] Arango’s unified architecture eliminates the overhead of moving data between systems.
[src:arangodb/documentation] Replace dozens of bolted-together components with one governed platform.
[src:arangodb/documentation] Less infrastructure to build, maintain, and debug.
[src:arangodb/documentation] A Frankenstack makes your team do all the work: build the graph, tune the retrieval, write queries across multiple systems.
[src:arangodb/documentation] Arango automates the three hardest parts.
[src:arangodb/documentation] Most knowledge graph projects spend months on ontology design before anything ships.
[src:arangodb/documentation] Arango AutoGraph ingests your enterprise data and automatically builds a governed knowledge graph: the foundation of your live contextual data layer.
[src:arangodb/documentation] Most platforms store your data and hope retrieval sorts it out.
